{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/post/github-api/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>前几天，在 V2EX 看见有人用 Github API 基于python实现了一个图床。于是我决定用 nodejs 也实现一个类似功能。首先我看有没现成的第三方库，在 <a href=\"https://developer.github.com/libraries/\">Libraries | GitHub Developer Guide</a> 我发现有五个跟 javascript 相关的库：  </p>\n<!-- more -->\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vitzy/imue/master/imgs/github-api-js.png\" alt=\"github-api-js\"> </p>\n<p>经调研发现 <a href=\"https://github.com/michael/github\">GitHub.js wrapper around the GitHub API</a> 比较好入手，基本将 Github API 全都实现了，并且封装了自己的接口，但是缺点还是有的，文档写的不太详细。然后就开始看它的文档，其中 Repository 的 writeFile() 方法就是上传文件的函数。<br>\n其中 writeFile():  </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vitzy/imue/master/imgs/github-api-writeFile-2.3.0.png\" alt=\"github-api-writeFile-2.3.0\">  </p>\n<p>先在这里贴出代码( ECMAScript 2015 标准)： </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">//导入github-api</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> GitHub <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"github-api\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> fs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"fs\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> gh <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">GitHub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\ttoken<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;your personal token>'</span><span class=\"token comment\">//这里采用token认证</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> branch <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;branch_name>'</span><span class=\"token comment\">//eg. master</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ufilePath <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;repo_path>'</span><span class=\"token comment\">//eg. images/</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//{master}/xxx.jpg</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ufileName <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;file_name>'</span><span class=\"token comment\">//eg. xxx.jpg</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> commit <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'here i am'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> user <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;user name>'</span><span class=\"token comment\">//用户名</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> repo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;repository name>'</span><span class=\"token comment\">//仓库名</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> re <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> gh<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getRepo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>user<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>repo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//同步读取文件</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> imageBlob <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> fs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">readFileSync</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'&lt;filepath>'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//base64编码</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> imageB64 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> imageBlob<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'base64'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//ascii编码</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//utf8编码也可以，只不过有些浪费。</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> imageB64<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ascii'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//author:{},</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//commiter:{},</span>\n    encode<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nre<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">writeFile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>branch<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> ufilePath <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> ufileName<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> data <span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> commit<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token operator\">===</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\tconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://cdn.rawgit.com/</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>user<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">/</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>repo<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">/</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>branch<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">/</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>ufilePath<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>ufileName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>这其中的关键就是编码问题， GitHub Contents API 要求 content 是 base64 编码。 </p>\n<p>​\t</p>","excerpt":"前几天，在 V2EX 看见有人用 Github API 基于python实现了一个图床。于是我决定用 nodejs 也实现一个类似功能。首先我看有没现成的第三方库，在 Libraries | GitHub Developer Guide 我发现有五个跟 javascript…","frontmatter":{"date":"10月08, 2016","title":"用 Github API 上传文件的方法","tags":["Javascript","Github"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/post/github-api/","prev":{"slug":"/post/rsa/","title":"非对称加密( RSA )数据传送的实战"},"next":{"slug":"/post/progressive-encoding-jpeg/","title":"生成渐进式 jpeg"}}}}